TestMultipleModifiersCompose
/ Verifies that cache + error modifiers compose correctly on one action.
/ Both reads use the same explicit cache key so the second hits the cache
/ even after the file is deleted.
- save 'testdata/compose_test.txt' with content 'hello compose'
- read file 'testdata/compose_test.txt'
    cache for 60 seconds key='compose-key'
    on error ignore
    write to %result%
- assert %result% equals 'hello compose'
- delete file 'testdata/compose_test.txt'
/ Second read should come from cache even though file is deleted
- read file 'testdata/compose_test.txt'
    cache for 60 seconds key='compose-key'
    on error ignore
    write to %cachedResult%
- assert %cachedResult% equals 'hello compose'
